{"tid":2422314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權： BioNTech延後到港 特首及局長接種科興後並無不適 籲公務員及其家人踴躍接種","createTime":"2021-02-25T06:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T06:38:53.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77e00c015ff6da3bf668015cfda9d0a82421265e","tid":2422314,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"聶德權料BioNTech疫苗短期運抵 籲公務員踴躍接種<br />\n<br />\nBioNTech疫苗未能在今日抵港，公務員事務局局長聶德權預計，疫苗會在短時間內運抵香港，政府存收妥當後，社區疫苗接種中心隨即會提供接種服務。聶德權向公務員發信，指局方月初邀請各常任秘書長和部門首長，提名公務員支援疫苗接種中心行政工作，已收到逾千個提名，令人鼓舞；他說，上周行政長官和司局長已經接種科興疫苗，過程簡單順利，沒有任何不適，呼籲公務員與家人踴躍報名接種疫苗，帶動社會參與。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權又說，政府多次封區檢測行動共調動1.2萬人次公務員參與，感謝他們配合政府各項防疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380549&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=91db7720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380549</a>"},{"pid":"654ac0cad41de45b5cd01a1b602241b474e24744","tid":2422314,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"睇下幾時中武肺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce1b89f915c8db595eb4bd1a88c2ac76e744db9","tid":2422314,"uid":31773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"打完第二飛好除口罩四圍走"},{"pid":"127d7ce666246b2a2ae73f9438ca65980af06f29","tid":2422314,"uid":20815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"梗係無不適啦，根本無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d481d0ec49b488c9bef281ee16cc426a547303ef","tid":2422314,"uid":50526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"打完咪繼續要安心出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860801dd79a379af8c1e85b904429898c0f695cc","tid":2422314,"uid":284855,"like":0,"di